### C3. Hardcoded test devices in production component

**File**: [other-devices-panel.component.ts](file:///home/nurlansarkhanov/Desktop/code/Revelton/thingsboard-extention/src/app/components/revelton-tb-extension-dashboard/features/other-devices-panel/other-devices-panel.component.ts#L157-L172)

```typescript
/** Hardcoded test device — remove once real data renders correctly */
readonly testDevice = {
  name: "trv_office_1",
  type: "Thermostat",
  // ...fake data
};
```

Test fixtures left in production code. If referenced in the template, users see phantom devices.

> [!CAUTION]
> **Fix**: Remove `testDevice` and `testDevice2` entirely.

