### C6. Hardcoded weather coordinates

**File**: [revelton-hotel.component.ts](file:///home/nurlansarkhanov/Desktop/code/Revelton/thingsboard-extention/src/app/components/revelton-tb-extension-dashboard/features/hotel-dashboard/revelton-hotel.component.ts#L538-L540)

```typescript
const url = "https://api.open-meteo.com/v1/forecast?latitude=50.2327&longitude=12.8712&current_weather=true";
```

Coordinates are for Karlovy Vary. Any other deployment shows wrong weather.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Fix**: Make coordinates configurable via widget settings.

